I also have a companion website. It's on GitHub that has some more examples and the slides

00:18:11.619 --> 00:18:21.420
from this talk. Thank you so much.

00:18:21.420 --> 00:18:28.420
I think we have time for one question. So how would you suggest someone goes about...

00:18:28.420 --> 00:18:50.420
Yeah. Oh, there we go. Okay. So someone that wants to go about starting with a small test

